name: Vintage Black & Yellow Floral Print Clutch Purse
description: This beautiful black and yellow vintage floral fabric clutch with remnant black satin interior, comes with covered button decoration and magnetic snap for easy access. This retro styled clutch purse is designed and hand made in Melbourne by Miyuki Mardon. Made from vintage and remnant fabrics, it is a limited edition design. Measuring 27X17cm/10.6"X6.7"(approx), it is perfect for carrying all your essentials for a special occasion. Great for that splash of vintage.

name: tic tac toe sunglass case
description:
This fabulous fabric sunglass case in blue, red & white retro dot pattern  is a great little accessory to keep your sunglasses/specs in one piece and scratch free in your purse or handbag. 
It features a simple flex frame opening for ease of use with a maximum width of opening of 9cm. Total size being 10 X 21cm. It folds flat when not use, and is very lightweight, so takes up no space at all.
Fits most standard sunglass cases. Larger 12cm wide cases available on request. POA.
